{"tid":1259563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明報標題誤導，想標籤遊行人士係殺人犯","createTime":"2019-06-26T15:13:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T15:53:20.000Z","uid":10141,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9fe09d16b8efedae33229268c76edea334f18acb","tid":1259563,"uid":10141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T15:13:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">6‧16金鐘悼墮樓示威者後　六旬漢天星碼頭疑遭遊行男子推跌亡 (21:55)</span><br />\n<br />\n民陣6月16日發起反《逃犯條例》修訂遊行，當晚10時許，一名六旬男子被發現倒臥在中環天星碼頭對出，送往瑪麗醫院治理，兩日後不治。驗屍報告顯示，他的後腦有一度13厘米裂痕。<br />\n<br />\n警方經調查後，事主當晚曾與另一名男子因排隊上船發生糾紛，被人推倒在地上，後腦着地。警方今日（26日）在屯門區拘捕一名26歲男子，涉嫌謀殺，初步有人承認與案有關。港島總區重案組總督察冼國明稱，二人不相識，事件不涉武器。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，該六旬男子當日到太古廣場，悼念前一晚在該商場高處墮下的男子，而26歲男子則剛完成民陣的遊行，二人當時正排隊準備乘船過海。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母明報<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a7ab245e27cd6ed6db4d1f1c1c3aebcda1562c","tid":1259563,"uid":10141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T15:42:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8143f0ccb569f8c3b6b6ba87ccfbf00e22ada94","tid":1259563,"uid":18642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T15:45:09.000Z","msg":"推 比多啲人見到"},{"pid":"a229a3efea9b8b0ba934009c6bd39ce58ab1d506","tid":1259563,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T15:46:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d05c1bf5469d60a86d80b4d5de2b464b256e2d0","tid":1259563,"uid